text: Neptunea polycostata is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. There is one subspecies: Neptunea polycostata aino Fraussen & Terryn, 2007 (synonym: Neptunea polycostata var. sculpturata Golikov, 1963) ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1955 Category:Marine gastropods
title: Neptunea polycostata
